    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In a glorious past, the kingdom of Meritons shone with wisdom and prosperity. But after centuries, the whole dynasty's been falling apart. The governance of the kingdom has crumbled, injustices have multiplied, and many citizens have been forced to leave a system that has become unfair and outdated.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/07e31e2fb8f4d2a981aa9625a56489ac.poster.avif?t=1751636750\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/07e31e2fb8f4d2a981aa9625a56489ac.webm?t=1751636750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/07e31e2fb8f4d2a981aa9625a56489ac.mp4?t=1751636750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You joined a small group in a camp near the city.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To survive, we’ll have to help each other and stick to the camp rules. Food, water, electricity, cleaning, resource management and rat hunting. Everything counts!</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/56ac80fa609ba9408ddb3c352756d885.poster.avif?t=1751636750\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/56ac80fa609ba9408ddb3c352756d885.webm?t=1751636750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/56ac80fa609ba9408ddb3c352756d885.mp4?t=1751636750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>The camp’s really basic, we’ll need to upgrade it if we want to survive the winters. You’ll help explore and discover new tools and techniques to craft improvements. From shelter insulation to vegetable gardening to electrical systems, there's plenty to do!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/68f17e5d6a01edfad1be0e2e5aa2e861.avif?t=1751636750\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Outcasts, but not alone! You’ll have plenty of missions to gain experience. Team up with your campmates for the riskiest tasks. High risk, high reward.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/7f6e37b653e8fcb6809699b980fe665c.avif?t=1751636750\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resources are running low, and the competition outside the camp is brutal. Don’t let anyone push you around. You're going to have to fight!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320630/extras/c2150585bdb574b72a8e10b010d80ef0.avif?t=1751636750\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
